snippet.title: IMPOSSIBLE ROAD Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
IMPOSSIBLE ROAD is a pure, minimal arcade game about risk, reward, and roller coasters.

Guide THE VESSEL down the roller coaster-like track at incredible speeds, scoring for each gate you make it through. Navigate hair-pin bends, jumps, banked curves and adverse camber in the quest for the perfect line.
